\s YESU UMWAMI ARAVUGA ATI
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Yesu Umwami Aravuga Ati:\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd uwizera akabatizwa uwo niwe uzakizwa utizera azacirwaho iteka kwizera bizanwa no kumva kumva ijambo ry’Imana kwizera ko Yesu kristo ar’umwami n’umukiza wawe. \bd*
\pc \bdit Uuradukunda, Yesu Waradukunze Mana udukomereze muri urwo Rukundo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Abamwizeye bose bakizera Izina \bd*\bd Rye \bd*\bd Yabahaye ubushobozi bwo kuba abana b’Imana, none mugenzi wanjye ni wumv’ijwi uyumunsi ntiwinangir’umutima niwe nzira Ukuri n’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd bugingo. \bd*
\pc \bdit Uuradukunda, Yesu Waradukunze Mana udukomereze muri urwo Rukundo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Yesu yatumy’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd ntumwa ze kujya mu mahanga yose bahindura abantu kuba abagishwa babigisha \bd*\bd Ubutumwa \bd*\bd bwiza. Abizera mubabatize mu \bd*\bd Izina \bd*\bd rya \bd*\bd Data \bd*\bd wa twese \bd*\bd Umwana \bd*\bd n’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd mwuka \bd*\bd Wera \bd*\bd mubigisha kwitondera ibyo nababwiye. \bd*
\pc \bdit Uuradukunda, Yesu Waradukunze Mana udukomereze muri urwo Rukundo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ababwira gutegereza \bd*\bd Imbaraga \bd*\bd z’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd mwuka \bd*\bd Wera \bd*\bd ku munsi wa \bd*\bd Pantekoste Isezerano \bd*\bd rirasohora, babwiriza \bd*\bd Ubutumwa \bd*\bd bwiza benshi bizera \bd*\bd Umukiza \bd*\bd babatizwa mu \bd*\bd Izina \bd*\bd rya Yesu nabo bahabwa \bd*\bd Umwuka Wera\bd*\bd . \bd*
\pc \bdit Uuradukunda, Yesu Waradukunze Mana udukomereze muri urwo Rukundo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ibyavuzwe mu mategeko ibyahanuwe no muri zaburi byasohoye kuri Kristo \bd*\bd Yarabambwe\bd*\bd , \bd*\bd Arahambwa\bd*\bd , \bd*\bd Arazuka\bd*\bd , none \bd*\bd Aratwungur’ubwengwe \bd*\bd ngo dusobanukirwe ibyanditswe kwihana no kubabarirwa bibwirwa amahanga mw’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd zina \bd*\bd Rye\bd*\bd . \bd*
\pc \bdit Uuradukunda, Yesu Waradukunze Mana udukomereze muri urwo Rukundo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Wabatijwe mu mazina atatu mu mazi menshi cyangwa ku gahanga haba mu \bd*\bd Izina \bd*\bd rya Yesu, uri mu idini siko kwizera; hariho \bd*\bd Itorero \bd*\bd rimwe, Imana \bd*\bd Imwe \bd*\bd n’\bd*\bd U\bd*\bd mubatizo umwe hariho kwizera kumwe ngwino ubatizwe mu \bd*\bd Izina \bd*\bd rya Yesu. \bd*
\pc \bdit Uuradukunda, Yesu Waradukunze Mana udukomereze muri urwo Rukundo.\bdit*
